\c 19
\s Ukuphenduka kukaZakewu
\p
\v 1 Wathi \add uJesu\add* engena, wadabula eJeriko\x + 18.35. Mat. 20.29.\x*.
\v 2 Njalo khangela, kwakukhona indoda eyayithiwa nguZakewu ngebizo\x + Ezra 2.9. Neh. 3.20. 7.14.\x*; owayeyinduna yabathelisi, njalo wayenothile;
\v 3 wadinga ukubona uJesu ukuthi ungubani\x + Mat. 25.24.\x*, kodwa kazange enelise ngenxa yexuku, ngoba wayelesithombo esifitshane\x + 2.52.\x*.
\v 4 Wasegijimela phambili wakhwela emkhiweni wesikhamore ukuze ambone\x + 1 Lan. 27.28. Luka 17.6.\x*; ngoba wayezadlula ngaleyo\add ndlela\add*.
\v 5 Kwathi uJesu efika kuleyondawo, wakhangela phezulu wambona, wathi kuye: Zakewu, phangisa wehle; ngoba lamuhla ngimele ukuhlala endlini yakho\x + Joha. 1.38.\x*.
\v 6 Wasephangisa wehla, wamemukela ethokoza\x + 10.38.\x*.
\v 7 Futhi bonke be\add ku\add*bona basola\x + 15.2.\x*, besithi: Ungene\x + 15.2.\x* wethekelela indoda eyisoni\x + 9.12.\x*.
\v 8 Kodwa uZakewu wema wathi eNkosini: Khangela, ingxenye yempahla yami, Nkosi, ngiyipha abayanga; kuthi uba ngimthathele umuntu\x + 3.14.\x* ulutho ngobuqili\x + 3.14.\x*, ngi\add lu\add*buyisela luphindwe kane\x + Eks. 22.1. 2 Sam. 12.6.\x*.
\v 9 UJesu wasesithi kuye: Lamuhla usindiso lufikile kulindlu, ngoba\x + 5.14. 7.5. Eks. 18.4.\x* laye\x + 3.8. 16.24,30. Roma 4.11,12,16. Gal. 3.7.\x* uyindodana kaAbrahama\x + 13.16.\x*.
\v 10 Ngoba iNdodana yomuntu\x + Mat. 18.11.\x* ize ukudinga lokusindisa okulahlekileyo\x + Mat. 18.12. Joha. 4.23.\x*.
\s Umfanekiso wemali
\p
\v 11 Kwathi besizwa lezizinto, wengezelela watsho umfanekiso, ngoba wayeseduze leJerusalema\x + 20.11,12. Seb. 12.3.\x*, la\add ngoba\add* babecabanga ukuthi umbuso kaNkulunkulu uzahle ubonakaliswe\x + 17.20. Seb. 1.6.\x*.
\v 12 Wasesithi-ke: Umuntu\x + 1 Kor. 1.26.\x* othile\x + Mat. 25.14-30.\x* oyisikhulu waya elizweni elikhatshana, ukuzemukelela umbuso, aphinde abuye\x + Mark. 13.34.\x*.
\v 13 Wasebiza inceku zakhe ezilitshumi, wazinika impondo ezilitshumi\x + Mat. 25.1.\x*, wathi kuzo: Sebenzani ngemali ngize ngibuye.
\v 14 Kodwa izakhamizi zakhe zamzonda, zathuma amanxusa emva kwakhe, zisithi: Kasithandi ukuthi lo asibuse\x + Joha. 1.11.\x*.
\v 15 Kwasekusithi esebuyile esewemukele umbuso, wathi azibizelwe kuye lezozinceku, ayezinike imali, ukuze azi ukuthi yileyo laleyo izuzeni ngokuthengiselana.
\v 16 Kweza-ke eyokuqala, yathi: Nkosi, impondo yakho izuze impondo ezilitshumi.
\v 17 Wasesithi kuyo: Kuhle, nceku elungileyo\x + 6.10. Mat. 25.21.\x*; lokhu uthembekile kokuncinyanyana, woba lamandla phezu kwemizi elitshumi\x + 19.13.\x*.
\v 18 Kwasekusiza eyesibili, yathi: Nkosi, impondo yakho yenze impondo ezinhlanu.
\v 19 Wasesithi lakuyo: Lawe woba phezu kwemizi emihlanu.
\v 20 Kwasekusiza enye, isithi: Nkosi, khangela impondo yakho, engayibeka elenjini\x + Joha. 11.44. 20.7. Seb. 19.12.\x*;
\v 21 ngoba bengikwesaba\x + Mat. 25.24.\x*, ngoba ungumuntu olukhuni; uthatha lokho ongakubekanga, futhi uvune lokho ongakuhlanyelanga.
\v 22 Wasesithi kuyo: Ngizakugweba \add ngoku\add*vela emlonyeni wakho, nceku embi\x + 2 Sam. 1.16. Jobe 15.6.\x*. Ubusazi\x + Mat. 25.26.\x* ukuthi mina ngingumuntu olukhuni, othatha lokho engingakubekanga, futhi avune lokho engingakuhlanyelanga;
\v 23 ngakho kungani ungafakanga imali yami ebhanga\x + Mat. 21.12.\x*, kuthi-ke mina ekufikeni kwami ngiyithathe\x + 3.13.\x* kanye lenzuzo\x + Mat. 25.27.\x*?
\v 24 Wasesithi kulabo ababemi khona: Memukeni impondo, li\add yi\add*nike lowo olempondo ezilitshumi.
\v 25 Kodwa bathi kuye: Nkosi, lowo ulempondo ezilitshumi.
\v 26 Ngoba ngithi kini: Wonke olakho uzaphiwa; kodwa lowo ongelakho, uzakwemukwa lalokho alakho\x + Mat. 13.12.\x*.
\v 27 Kodwa lezozitha zami, ebezingathandi ukuthi ngizibuse\x + 19.14.\x*, \add zi\add*letheni lapha, li\add zi\add*bulale phambi kwami\x + 1 Sam. 11.12. Mat. 22.7. Luka 20.16.\x*.
\s UJesu ungena eJerusalema
\p
\v 28 Esetshilo lezizinto, wahamba phambili\x + Mark. 10.32. Luka 13.22.\x*, esenyukela eJerusalema\x + 2.4.\x*.
\p
\v 29 Kwasekusithi esondela eBetfage leBethani entabeni okuthiwa ngeyeMihlwathi, wathuma ababili kubafundi bakhe,
\v 30 esithi: Hambani liye emzaneni okhangelene \add lani\add*; lizakuthi lingena kuwo lifice ithole likababhemi libotshiwe, okungazanga kuhlale kulo muntu; lilikhulule li\add li\add*lethe.
\v 31 Uba umuntu elibuza esithi: Li\add li\add*khululelani? Lizakutsho njalo kuye ukuthi: INkosi iyaliswela.
\v 32 Ababethunyiwe bahamba-ke bafica kunjengoba ebatshelile\x + Mat. 21.1-11. Mark. 11.1-10.\x*.
\v 33 Kuthe besalikhulula ithole, abaninilo bathi kubo: Lilikhululelani ithole\x + Mark. 11.5.\x*?
\v 34 Bona basebesithi: INkosi iyaliswela.
\v 35 Basebeliletha kuJesu; baphosela izembatho zabo phezu kwethole likababhemi, bamkhweza uJesu kulo.
\v 36 Kwathi ehamba, bendlala izembatho zabo phansi endleleni\x + Joha. 12.12-15.\x*.
\v 37 Kwathi khathesi esesondela ekwehleni kwentaba yeMihlwathi, ixuku lonke labafundi laqala ukuthokoza lokudumisa uNkulunkulu ngelizwi elikhulu\x + 18.43.\x* ngayo yonke imisebenzi yamandla eliyibonileyo\x + Joha. 12.17,18.\x*,
\v 38 lisithi: Ibusisiwe inkosi ezayo ebizweni leNkosi\x + Joha. 12.13. Mat. 25.34.\x*; ukuthula ezulwini, lenkazimulo kweliphezulu\x + 2.14.\x*.
\v 39 Labanye babaFarisi ababesexukwini bathi kuye: Mfundisi, khuza abafundi bakho\x + Mat. 21.15,16.\x*.
\v 40 Wasephendula wathi kubo: Ngithi kini, uba bethula laba, amatshe azamemeza\x + Hab. 2.11.\x*.
\p
\v 41 Kwathi esondela, ewubona umuzi\x + 19.37.\x*, wawukhalela\x + Joha. 11.35. Heb. 5.7.\x*,
\v 42 esithi: Kungathi ngabe wazile lawe, ngitsho ngalolusuku lwakho, izinto zokuthula kwakho; kodwa-ke khathesi zifihlakele emehlweni akho\x + 13.9. Tshu. 9.14.\x*.
\v 43 Ngoba insuku zizakwehlela phezu kwakho, lapho izitha zakho zizakwakhela umthangala\x + Isa. 29.3. 37.33. Jer. 6.6. Hez. 4.2. 26.8.\x* zikugombolozele, zikuzingelezele\x + 21.20.\x*, zikuvimbele inhlangothi zonke\x + Isa. 29.4.\x*,
\v 44 zikudilizele phansi wena labantwana bakho\x + 1.64.\x* abaphakathi kwakho, zingatshiyi ilitshe phezu kwelitshe phakathi kwakho\x + Mark. 13.2. Luka 21.6. Mat. 24.2.\x*; ngoba ungasazanga isikhathi\x + Dan. 9.24.\x* sokuhanjelwa kwakho\x + 1 Pet. 2.12. Luka 1.68,78. Jobe 10.12. Jer. 6.6.\x*.
\s Ukuhlanjululwa kwethempeli
\p
\v 45 Wasengena ethempelini, waqala ukuxotsha abathengisayo kulo, labathengayo\x + Mat. 21.12,13,16. Mark. 11.15,17,18. Joha. 2.13-17.\x*,
\v 46 esithi kubo: Kulotshiwe \add ukuthi\add*: Indlu yami yindlu yomkhuleko\x + Isa. 56.7.\x*; kodwa lina liyenze ubhalu lwabaphangi\x + Jer. 7.11.\x*.
\p
\v 47 Njalo wayefundisa ethempelini insuku zonke\x + 20.1. Mat. 26.55.\x*; kodwa abapristi abakhulu lababhali\x + Mark. 11.18. Joha. 7.19. Mat. 21.46. Luka 20.19.\x* lenduna zabantu badinga ukumbulala;
\v 48 kodwa kabatholanga abangakwenza, ngoba abantu bonke banamathela kuye be\add m\add*lalela\x + Mark. 6.21.\x*.